<body>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>This Chrome extension, <strong>Address to Phone Swapper</strong>, does not collect, store, or share any personal information or user data.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>It does <strong>not</strong> track user activity.</li>
    <li>It does <strong>not</strong> collect or transmit any data.</li>
    <li>It does <strong>not</strong> store any data locally or remotely.</li>
    <li>It does <strong>not</strong> use any third-party APIs or remote code.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>The extension only runs a local script when the user clicks the "Run" button, which modifies fields on the currently active web page. It does not log or save any information from the page.</p>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, feel free to reach out to the developer.</p>
</body>
